name: The Lost Ones #2
description: This is the poor, unfortunate soul of a wayward wanderer, who strayed to far from the path. It is now in the possession of a Spectral Pukwudgie, there are Six of these ghostly beasts lurking in Umbra. A Spectral Pukwudgie can only master one soul orb at a time. 10/05/2021 Sinner Crypto
